      <title>新加坡航空在致命乱流后改变安全带规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/singapore-airlines-changes-seatbelt-sign-rules-after-fatal-turbulence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候，新加坡航空从伦敦起飞的航班上，一名乘客死亡，数十人受伤，飞机遭遇湍流，因此采取了更严格的客舱限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/singapore-airlines-changes-seatbelt-sign-rules-after-fatal-turbulence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
