      <title>韩国AI芯片股暴涨1200%考验投资者神经</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/a-1-200-surge-tests-nerves-of-investors-in-korean-ai-chip-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 2022 年底以来，韩美半导体公司 (Hanmi Semiconductor Co.) 股价上涨近 1,200%，一些投资者在估值过高的情况下寻求套现。]]></description>
